{
  "stem": "1061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I ascribe it really to my age, rather than to my understanding of the situation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[DRINKS] Do you remember other members of your extended family?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, my grandmother, who I refer to my mother's mother, her name was Sarah Tenenblum, lived about 20 miles away from us in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she and-- had two daughters that weren't yet married, my Aunt Regina, after whom I am-- I have a name, and my-- and Anjia owned a printing shop.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], as we called her, grandma, [INAUDIBLE], used to invite each one of us, of the three sisters, for a stay of a week or two with her alone.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was religious, and she felt she would supplement the religious education that perhaps my mother did not supply to the extent that she like-- would have liked it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And well, my times spent with the grandmother were just absolutely out of this world, for me, at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, we're talking about my being eight or nine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would go, of course be taken into the printing shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was allowed to go to the-- where the facility, the operation of the-- of the-- of the painting was taking place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was allowed to-- to touch the machinery because the gentleman who worked in the back knew me, and of course they-- they wanted to impress me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then on the way home-- before I would go home, I would collect a bag of-- they would collect it for me, you know, when they would print, let's say, posters.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would cut them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all of the thing-- the paper strips that would fall off would be put in a bag.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
